You are in a Dining Room.
It's the dining room, and its a mess. You don't remember much of the events of last night, and as you explore more of your house, your beginning to wonder why its a mess, all except for your room. And now that your thinking about it more, why was your door locked? Oh well. You see your table turned, and there are some glass plates broken on the floor. Some food is flung on the walls. Wait a minute, something is missing. Where the hell are your dining chairs?!
