You are in a Front yard.
This is your front yard. There is a mailbox, and a welcome mat. At the gate, there is also a "unicornium." The ugly horned beast is eyeing you down, but not advancing or retreating.
You can go south or north.
You can see a mailbox and an Unicornium.
> open mailbox

> open mailbox
You open it.
It contains a letter.
> x letter

> x letter
Dear Samuel,

    You may have already figured it out, but it is now time to open your chest. You should be in the past, ancient times. You are my son, and I am your mother, so I hate to say this but we need a hero, and it is you. A horrible event will happen soon, and you need to stop it. It will be risky, but I know you can do it.
    This is because you, Sam, are different from the others. You were given a gift. A powerful, yet dangerous gift. Under control, it can do marvelous things, but in chaos, it can destroy any one or thing, even you. This power you possess is an ancient one. You can control the very thing that keeps our universe together. Your power is that of magic. Sam, you are a wizard.
    With your powers, you will be able to save our world, and take evil's grasp off it. Go, Sam, and may sword and spell be with you on your quest.

Love forever,
Mom
