You are in a Front yard.
This is your front yard. There is a mailbox, and a welcome mat.
You can go south or north.
You can see a mailbox (containing a letter).
Now that you are more attentive to your surroundings, you begin to notice a lot is different, and you mean a lot. The city buildings that were all around you are missing, and there is no trace of them. The busy road is gone, and the big billboard by your house has vanished. In fact, the only thing here is a forest, and you're in the middle of it, with your front yard the only clearing in sight. There seems to be a path going north, guess its your only option, if you're going to find out what this big event is.
> north

> north

You are in a Clearing.
A big clearing in front of your house. Around it, are trees, and they don't seem to end. The only path through the trees lies to the north. A sign ahead, pointing down the path says "Deseron." Must be the name of a town. A sign on the same post points to your house and says "Domum Heroum." Wonder what that means. But it's a part of the ancient language, or so it seems. That sign must have some magical effect here.
You can go south or north.
