You are in a Deseron.
A very small town, with people traveling to and fro between the 7 buildings you see. No one pays any attention to you as you walk around. You see 6 shops, and one weird building. You've only seen three people go in, but a lot come out. You should probably look at the other shops before you enter this mysterious building. The six shops you saw included a blacksmith to the south, alchemy lab to the south west, library to the west, tavern to the north west, armory to the north, and a general store to the north east. The weird building is to the east.
