You are in a Medieval Mart.
The name of this store confuses the hell out of you, for obvious reasons. Anyway, the store seems to be filled with all the common items you'd need for a typical day at home. There's food, some weird toys, some furniture stuff, clothes, and more. All you'd really need from here is what's in the corner of the store. The adventurers gear. Looks like there is rope, a grapple hook, a compass, a map of some place, and some "crustulum."
