You can see a grappling hook with rope, a compass, a Map, a Crustulum and a Shop keeper.
> x map

> x map
A map of a place your unfamiliar with. Maybe it could be useful, but who knows. From the looks of it, it seems to be a map of a nearby valley. There are four major marks on the map. The first has the fire symbol, and says "Volcano here, venture with caution." The second has the symbol of water, and says "Lake here, do not swim." The next mark is the symbol for earth, and it says "Strange rocks, watch for chasm." The last mark is the air symbol, and says "Large storms here, seeming to come from nearby cave." You want to take it, but its worth 5 drabble. Expensive map. You want it so bad though...
