The old man introduces himself as a fellow wizard, except he opens and closes portals, instead of casting elemental magic. He has a portal to the valley on that map you stole. He says it will take you to the spot marked on your map that corresponds to your element. He wishes you farewell, and luck on your travels, and urges you to go into the portal.
