> x portal to valley
You see a mass of swirling purples, all following an ovular shape.
> enter portal to valley

> enter portal to valley
You walk through, and immediately feel sick. The purple seems to pick you up, and throw you into the valley scene below. You land straight on your feet, and you then discover..... there's no heading back.

